[
    {
        "text": "We're going to take a look at",
        "start": 0.0,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "some more rules for how to pronounce",
        "start": 1.04,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "words ending with silent 'e' today.",
        "start": 2.88,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Firstly, the letters 'c' and 'g' can have",
        "start": 5.44,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "hard consonant sounds like /k/ and /g/.",
        "start": 8.8,
        "duration": 4.048
    },
    {
        "text": "However, when the word ends with a",
        "start": 12.848,
        "duration": 1.952
    },
    {
        "text": "silent 'e' it changes the pronunciation",
        "start": 14.8,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "of these consonants.",
        "start": 17.76,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "'C' and 'g' become soft consonant sounds",
        "start": 19.36,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "/s/ and /ʤ/. So it's pronounced /mais/ not /maik/",
        "start": 22.56,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "and /keiʤ/ not /keig/. Another very similar rule",
        "start": 26.8,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "is for the pronunciation of 'th'.",
        "start": 30.24,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "When a word ends with 'th' and then a silent 'e',",
        "start": 33.12,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "it changes from a /θ/ sound to a /ð/ sound.",
        "start": 37.2,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "The most common example of this",
        "start": 41.36,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "is the word 'the'.",
        "start": 43.12,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "It's pronounced with a /ð/ sound.",
        "start": 44.4,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Some other examples include",
        "start": 46.8,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "'breath' and 'breathe' and 'bath' and 'bathe'.",
        "start": 48.4,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "These nice and easy rules should help",
        "start": 51.76,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "you when pronouncing new words.",
        "start": 54.08,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Just remember that the silent 'e'",
        "start": 55.92,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "changes pronunciation.",
        "start": 58.08,
        "duration": 1.6
    }
]